1 Week Ago SaharaReporters earlier reported that Ekweremadu had approached Nigeria’s Federal High Court, Abuja to compel the National Identity Management Commission (NIMC) to provide a certified copy of the victim’s information to the UK Court to establish his real age.  The Commission denied the request but later requested to send the victim’s information to the Attorney General of the Federation and Minister of Justice (AGF) for onward transmission to the UK Court. See Also






